1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,690
[Episode 27]

2
00:00:11,540 --> 00:00:14,960
I've already told you everything
I confessed all I know

3
00:00:15,210 --> 00:00:16,970
What more do you want from me?

4
00:00:28,930 --> 00:00:30,050
You slut

5
00:00:31,690 --> 00:00:36,490
So the acne-faced Bin
and that product reviewer Bin

6
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:38,330
are actually the same person

7
00:00:40,850 --> 00:00:43,170
-Taji-
-Yes, boss

8
00:00:43,610 --> 00:00:46,020
Let's say you have a friend

9
00:00:46,590 --> 00:00:49,090
But because of a misunderstanding

10
00:00:49,330 --> 00:00:51,130
Just because
you said some hurtful things

11
00:00:51,130 --> 00:00:54,830
That left a shadow on his life

12
00:00:55,410 --> 00:00:56,770
What would you do?

13
00:00:59,770 --> 00:01:02,300
Is this about a friend or a lover, boss?

14
00:01:04,730 --> 00:01:07,190
Lover?
What nonsense are you talking about?

15
00:01:08,610 --> 00:01:10,610
Actually, it's pretty much the same

16
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:13,370
If it's a friend, an apology should be enough

17
00:01:13,370 --> 00:01:17,030
If they don't forgive you
then you just have to accept it. That's it

18
00:01:17,039 --> 00:01:19,700
-But if it's love...
-It is about a lover, right?

19
00:01:20,370 --> 00:01:24,220
You need to be persistent
Only persistence can conquer the world

20
00:01:24,730 --> 00:01:28,730
I mean, conquer
Mr. Bin's entire world

21
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:34,530
That's right
I must be persistent

22
00:01:35,289 --> 00:01:39,729
To monopolize
and rule Bin's entire world

23
00:01:41,050 --> 00:01:43,810
[To Be Continued]
